[RegisterPage] --(new user created as Manager)--> [LoginPage]
[LoginPage] --(credentials verified)--> [Backend returns JWT + user details]
--> [DashboardPage]

[DashboardPage] --> [Layout (Sidebar + Content)]
      |
      +-- If Manager --> (Dashboard, SellPage, PurchasePage, TransactionsPage)
      |
      +-- If Admin   --> (All Manager pages + CategoryPage, SupplierPage, ProductPage)

-------------------------------------------------------
